{"tid":1895952,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實大家喺屌泛民嘅同時有冇諗過揸撚住佢春袋叫佢做嘢","createTime":"2020-02-24T23:55:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-18T01:19:55.000Z","uid":44455,"like":24,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"93c0ceaabab28ec1d4c66ad9028414fe7d865c7a","tid":1895952,"uid":44455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T23:55:44.000Z","msg":"今日見到有人share呢個手足嘅page<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/UnitedCommunityHongKong/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FUnitedCommunityHongKong%2F&d=MxNsT%2FmsUjaXWzHBtsAqwUkSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=20aa9ee6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/UnitedCommunityHongKong/</a><br />\n話用五set提案夾鳩班議員等佢哋做野<br />\n<br />\n突然間諗起咁多年嚟我哋屌泛民，而就算我地手足唔投佢地，佢哋都依然可以入到去繼續賣港，<br />\n點解？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為總有D狀況外的左膠 盲投俾佢地 (甚至可能投票當買贖罪劵)<br />\n<br />\n簡單D講，總有D人唔係睇政見，唔係睇往績，真係睇你講自己好黃，俾多少少人血，個饅頭就可以出爐食得<br />\n當然有D含撚無得揀的又係一個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但既然泛民的存在呢家為止都係好亞視咁<br />\n咁除左屌泛民同含撚投票，點解我地唔搵方法夾佢哋個春袋<br />\n佢哋個春袋係乜？好簡單，就係票同面 (即係佢地口中的「民意」光環呀！)<br />\n<br />\n我地逼佢地公開響應呢5個提案，如果佢哋唔跟就同民意過唔去，就唔撚投俾佢哋<br />\n佢地入到去，我地仲要監察住佢地的投票，如果同競選承諾不乎就要佢地付出代價，要佢地無晒光環<br />\n<br />\n好簡單一句<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">就係要泛民表態，俾就算淺黃都有個指標要投就應該投邊個</span></span><br />\n泛民要搶票我地無法，但都要有佢地付出代價<br />\n<br />\n大家諗下，當泛民講的野都同我地口徑一致，到時如果港共要DQ，佢就會被更多話柄，到時就可以更加有料打國際戰線。<br />\n當然佢有本事連泛民都DQ埋，但我就唔信佢地可以DQ晒咁多本土的泛民的議員！<br />\n佢敢玩到咁，咁咪攬炒囉！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後當然都要講句<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n光復香港 時代革命！"},{"pid":"145042f8632809d33efa6c77e85cf62092867319","tid":1895952,"uid":44455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T23:56:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"24ad6baca19e16f224fa8bea6b5fa61beac9dc7c","tid":1895952,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T23:57:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33ddd4a703719ee0dcdb3059f5071e9eb7de040d","tid":1895952,"uid":281023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T23:58:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3a4d266f7f664f835e46efd42ef679a7a5edbd08","tid":1895952,"uid":281023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T23:59:07.000Z","msg":"退"},{"pid":"d18634a6674939914b9be347d6d623a56833de37","tid":1895952,"uid":88743,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T23:59:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=381863\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D381863&d=MxNsT%2FmsUjaXWzHBtsAqwUkSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=f87b8e46\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D381863&h=ffb59e69\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=381863</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3HXWKtX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3HXWKtX.jpg&h=43a3f5d9&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n白鴿黨算唔算表左態?"},{"pid":"34cae55245548b71613fdaf17b50505f5e15a884","tid":1895952,"uid":281023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T23:59:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"16914071b8c6a1223f3b5ede156d884a27a1eeb6","tid":1895952,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T00:04:15.000Z","msg":"特權法好似提過"},{"pid":"0fa73c3320940e703d7d687c0e400134cd98e98c","tid":1895952,"uid":125168,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T00:09:46.000Z","msg":"facebook個d 淺黃好buy泛民咁，會投票但無意